comments: Valanciunas (MEM) slightly extends his arms into Holiday's (IND) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position off-ball.
Holiday (IND) grabs Valaciunas' (MEM) arm and the contact affects Valanciunas' shot attempt in the post.
Bane (MEM) briefly places his hand to McConnell's (IND) front at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Sabonis (IND) makes marginal contact with Morant (MEM) as he brushes his arm at the end of his drive and does not affect his ability to gather.
Sabonis (IND) briefly grasps Valanciunas' (MEM) arm off-ball and does not affect his FOM.
Sabonis (IND) moves laterally toward Morant (MEM) and marginal contact occurs that he plays through during his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) makes marginal contact to LeVert's (IND) body after the release of his driving shot attempt.
McConnell (IND) moves laterally into Morant's (MEM) path and extends his leg, causing him to trip at the start of his drive.
LeVert (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bane (MEM) during his driving shot attempt.
Brogdon (IND) legally contests Morant's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Bane (MEM) makes contact with LeVert's (IND) arm and affects his control of the ball.
Bane (MEM) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
